{"tid":393181,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鍾意湯淺政明","createTime":"2017-09-09T05:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T08:42:08.000Z","uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"167c3386f1463f77bf09581db6e6a0ff33ff67e9","tid":393181,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"應該人人都睇過佢執導個套 蠟筆小新高叉魔王劇場版,<br />\n其實小丸子同小新套電視動畫佢都有份參與部份製作<br />\n<br />\n近年幾出名既美國動畫adventure time都有一集搵佢黎整<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/bonsaiho/1467861338-477426960.jpg?v=1467861338\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fbonsaiho%2F1467861338-477426960.jpg%3Fv%3D1467861338&h=332b6e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講下兩套我比較喜歡既動畫<br />\n<br />\n乒乓<br />\n就如其名就係講乒乓波<br />\n雖然呢套野畫風比較另類,<br />\n<img src=\"https://theelectricpress.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/akuma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheelectricpress.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F06%2Fakuma.jpg&h=a15d25d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係構圖同分鏡都非常有張力同動感<br />\n<img src=\"http://pa1.narvii.com/5660/fbe402fe1ebc15bd9bfd841a7034d346f6494f77_hq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpa1.narvii.com%2F5660%2Ffbe402fe1ebc15bd9bfd841a7034d346f6494f77_hq.gif&h=82a68931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇中一個主要角色係中國選手亦係全程用普通話配音,幾有心機<br />\n<br />\n四疊半神話大系<br />\n一套偏重佬味既動畫<br />\n主角升上大學一直好渴望cow返條女,享受現充既校園生活<br />\n所以諗啲屎橋加入啲社團cow女,<br />\n<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/dc92e713dabb6d40d90d2f960e57cdfb/tumblr_nwdmgpzTsw1uduh1yo1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fdc92e713dabb6d40d90d2f960e57cdfb%2Ftumblr_nwdmgpzTsw1uduh1yo1_500.gif&h=13fe8abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然套野有神話兩個字就梗係有啲奇幻成份<br />\n每集都係以唔同平行時空既主角加入唔同社團做開首,對呢方面有興趣既人可以睇睇,我覺得鍾意命運石之門既人都會喜歡呢套野<br />\n<br />\n今年湯淺政明都出左兩套電影<br />\n一套係同四疊半神話大系同樣由森見登美彥原作既 春宵苦短,少女前進吧!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tmeU9GFJW3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtmeU9GFJW3I&d=GDJagqiBaZJVenk1VeOmF%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=64716a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tmeU9GFJW3I</a><br />\n<br />\n另一套係<br />\n宣告黎明的露之歌 拎左今年法國安錫動畫展既長篇動畫獎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7YV54Z5i5Kw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7YV54Z5i5Kw&d=GDJagqiBaZJVenk1VeOmF%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=86672943\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7YV54Z5i5Kw</a><br />\n<br />\n兩套都有係台灣上映,唔知香港會唔會有得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bd81f86b642003fd4b9749d36a8c297761d9b1","tid":393181,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"唔記得加返個[火影]係前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b1f3bc071eb826b67a0a0227ec06d00e8ba6cc","tid":393181,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"四疊半中後段有幾集睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"ceae2ae2ef3e3cf76cf4ae0cfc2a722801e88e6c","tid":393181,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"adventure time我追哂咁多季<br />\nfinn 見返呀媽好感動<br />\n仲有jake揾返自我都好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51daa3e0fcd720541340130930be5ac46b599a4f","tid":393181,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"KAIBA睇過未<br />\n之前睇四疊半之後補，單係畫風已經好中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f577a65d3aeb531e8f33c45491cbad3808b2f02b","tid":393181,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>KAIBA睇過未<br />\n之前睇四疊半之後補，單係畫風已經好中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新個套宣告黎明的露之歌個畫面有少少似海馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6650d034b2d722412dfa2f1e0d8ec9461a01ec","tid":393181,"uid":48680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"鐘意 但太叫好唔叫座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n四疊半 同 蜂蜜與四葉草<br />\n 我認為每個高中毒撚必睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}